readable.content: A girl with a pink headband and blue shirt is drumming on blue plastic and metal bowls with chopsticks . A little asian girl banging on pans . A young Chinese girl playing the drums with two chopsticks , a pot , and a blue plastic bowl . A young girl with a pink headband hits a dish and pan with chopsticks . The child is using chopsticks on overturned kitchen items .
